  "body": "## What's Changed\r\n* chore(ci): use dd-sts for system-tests test optimization by @nccatoni in https://github.com/DataDog/datadog-lambda-python/pull/788\r\n* Remove system-tests pin by @nccatoni in https://github.com/DataDog/datadog-lambda-python/pull/801\r\n* Onzia/add us2 by @ojproductions in https://github.com/DataDog/datadog-lambda-python/pull/802\r\n* fix: pin ddtrace to <4.8.0 to avoid import errors by @brettlangdon in https://github.com/DataDog/datadog-lambda-python/pull/811\r\n* Replace use of _SpanPointer and AgentWriter by @rithikanarayan in https://github.com/DataDog/datadog-lambda-python/pull/812\r\n* ci: install upstream ddtrace wheel during PR-triggered unit tests by @purple4reina in https://github.com/DataDog/datadog-lambda-python/pull/813\r\n* Revert \"ci: install upstream ddtrace wheel during PR-triggered unit tests\" by @rithikanarayan in https://github.com/DataDog/datadog-lambda-python/pull/814\r\n* v8.125.0 by @ojproductions in https://github.com/DataDog/datadog-lambda-python/pull/819\r\n* Reintroduces `base_service` for Python Serverless Spans by @zarirhamza in https://github.com/DataDog/dd-trace-py/pull/17238\r\n\r\n>[!IMPORTANT]\r\n> For Python 3.8 and 3.9: `dd-trace-py` version is [v3.19.6](https://github.com/DataDog/dd-trace-py/releases/tag/v3.19.6)\r\n> For Python >= 3.10: `dd-trace-py` version is [v4.8.1](https://github.com/DataDog/dd-trace-py/releases/tag/v4.8.1)\r\n\r\n\r\n>[!IMPORTANT]\r\n> This layer is currently unavailable in aws region `me-south-1`, due to unrelated incidents\r\n\r\n```\r\n# AWS Commercial\r\narn:aws:lambda:<AWS_REGION>:464622532012:layer:Datadog-Python38:125\r\narn:aws:lambda:<AWS_REGION>:464622532012:layer:Datadog-Python38-ARM:125\r\narn:aws:lambda:<AWS_REGION>:464622532012:layer:Datadog-Python39:125\r\narn:aws:lambda:<AWS_REGION>:464622532012:layer:Datadog-Python39-ARM:125\r\narn:aws:lambda:<AWS_REGION>:464622532012:layer:Datadog-Python310:125\r\narn:aws:lambda:<AWS_REGION>:464622532012:layer:Datadog-Python310-ARM:125\r\narn:aws:lambda:<AWS_REGION>:464622532012:layer:Datadog-Python311:125\r\narn:aws:lambda:<AWS_REGION>:464622532012:layer:Datadog-Python311-ARM:125\r\narn:aws:lambda:<AWS_REGION>:464622532012:layer:Datadog-Python312:125\r\narn:aws:lambda:<AWS_REGION>:464622532012:layer:Datadog-Python312-ARM:125\r\narn:aws:lambda:<AWS_REGION>:464622532012:layer:Datadog-Python313:125\r\narn:aws:lambda:<AWS_REGION>:464622532012:layer:Datadog-Python313-ARM:125\r\narn:aws:lambda:<AWS_REGION>:464622532012:layer:Datadog-Python314:125\r\narn:aws:lambda:<AWS_REGION>:464622532012:layer:Datadog-Python314-ARM:125\r\n\r\n# AWS GovCloud \r\narn:aws-us-gov:lambda:us-gov-<AWS_REGION>:<ACCOUNT>:layer:Datadog-Python38:125\r\narn:aws-us-gov:lambda:us-gov-<AWS_REGION>:<ACCOUNT>:layer:Datadog-Python38-ARM:125\r\narn:aws-us-gov:lambda:us-gov-<AWS_REGION>:<ACCOUNT>:layer:Datadog-Python39:125\r\narn:aws-us-gov:lambda:us-gov-<AWS_REGION>:<ACCOUNT>:layer:Datadog-Python39-ARM:125\r\narn:aws-us-gov:lambda:us-gov-<AWS_REGION>:<ACCOUNT>:layer:Datadog-Python310:125\r\narn:aws-us-gov:lambda:us-gov-<AWS_REGION>:<ACCOUNT>:layer:Datadog-Python310-ARM:125\r\narn:aws-us-gov:lambda:us-gov-<AWS_REGION>:<ACCOUNT>:layer:Datadog-Python311:125\r\narn:aws-us-gov:lambda:us-gov-<AWS_REGION>:<ACCOUNT>:layer:Datadog-Python311-ARM:125\r\narn:aws-us-gov:lambda:us-gov-<AWS_REGION>:<ACCOUNT>:layer:Datadog-Python312:125\r\narn:aws-us-gov:lambda:us-gov-<AWS_REGION>:<ACCOUNT>:layer:Datadog-Python312-ARM:125\r\narn:aws-us-gov:lambda:us-gov-<AWS_REGION>:<ACCOUNT>:layer:Datadog-Python313:125\r\narn:aws-us-gov:lambda:us-gov-<AWS_REGION>:<ACCOUNT>:layer:Datadog-Python313-ARM:125\r\narn:aws-us-gov:lambda:us-gov-<AWS_REGION>:<ACCOUNT>:layer:Datadog-Python314:125\r\narn:aws-us-gov:lambda:us-gov-<AWS_REGION>:<ACCOUNT>:layer:Datadog-Python314-ARM:125\r\n\r\nACCOUNT =\r\n002406178527 for us1 environment\r\n486696501492 for us2 environment\r\n```\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/DataDog/datadog-lambda-python/compare/v